comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-24T12:25:27.480Z",codex,"No pm-cli or SDK changes required. This is a pure pm-changelog feature: the generator derives the type directory from item.type using a simple lowercase+plural rule."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-24T12:25:27.480Z",codex,"Requested to satisfy requirement: generated changelog must link to pm items with GitHub web-compatible links so users can click through to .toon file details."
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-05-24T12:25:27.480Z",codex,"pm stores items in type-specific subdirectories: .agents/pm/{issues,tasks,chores,features,epics}/. Always derive the subdir from item.type when constructing item URLs; never hardcode a single type directory."
